fields.label: All consultations with our GPs or Specialists will be bulk billed.
Any biopsies as recommended by the Medical Practitioner will be bulk billed.
Any treatment for skin cancers on our premises will be bulk billed.

groups.label: Any benign (non-cancerous) lesions which you request to be excised or treated on our premises will incur an out-of-pocket fee.
If you require any wound dressing consumables to continue your post-op care, there will be a fee of $10 per dressing.
*Please note that you will need a valid Medicare card and sign a Medicare assignment authorisation to be bulk billed or receive medical rebates from Medicare.
If you have any queries please discuss with our reception staff
